    <text type="letter">
        <body>


            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.01830.001.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">New Castle, Pa.</name>
                    <date when="1867-07-17">July 17.</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>My Dear Walt:</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>You have, I believe, in your hands certain charges against Judge Kelly of
                Idaho<!-- <ptr target="n0340"/> -->. His friends are <hi rend="underline">my</hi> friends, and
                while I do not know much of him personally, I nevertheless know his accuser,
                Delegate
                Holbrook<!--Edward Dexter Holbrook (1836-1870), a congressional delegate from Idaho Territory-->,
                to be a very bad man&#8212;one of the worst in the territory. It seems to me that
                nothing good or proper can come out of him. Do not misunderstand me, but if you can
                do anything for Judge K. to aid him, without compromising your duty, you will be
                doing me a <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.01830.003.jpg" type="verso"/>
                <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc.01830.002.jpg" type="recto"/> favor.</p>
            <p>I congratulate you, my dear fellow, on the great appreciation which <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#nnk">reaches</unclear>
                <!-- this was "readers" before -NNK -->
                <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#nnk">across</unclear>
                <!-- this was "again" before -NNK --> the <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#nnk">greatwater</unclear>
                <!-- this was "greatmaster" before -NNK --> to shake your hand. Your time is coming.
                The world is getting to be enlightened. I am already, in a worldly way, as I am in a
                spiritual way, <unclear reason="illegible" cert="medium" resp="#js">pious</unclear>
                to be considered</p>


            <closer>
                <salute>Your friend</salute>
                <signed><hi rend="underline">H. J. Ramsdell<!-- <ptr target="n0483"/> --></hi></signed>
            </closer>

